author: Harvinder Sidhu
title: AD: Save up to RM105,000 on an Audi with Euromobil
text:
Home » Special Coverage » Advertorial » AD: Save up to RM105,000 on an Audi with Euromobil AD: Save up to RM105,000 on an Audi with Euromobil 12 January 2017 4:21 pm / Comments are Disabled 
Looking for a new ride to enter the new year in style? Look no further, as Euromobil has just the deal for you. This weekend, January 14 and 15, Euromobil is offering savings of up to RM105,000* on a brand new Audi! 
On top of this, with every booking, customers will be entitled to Euromobil’s Spin the Wheel game to win further cash rebates worth up RM1,888* and many more attractive offers. The offers will be available at the DRB-HICOM Autofest 2017 at EON Complex, Glenmarie, as well as Audi Juru and Johor Bahru. 
Audi Approved :plus units will also be on auction at Autofest 2017, so be sure to head on over for more fantastic deals. Refer below for the respective addresses: 
DRB-HICOM Autofest 2017 EON Complex, No. 2, Persiaran Kerjaya, Taman Perindustrian Glenmarie,
